ft c-float -hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;3HlaGb&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;了解比价政策百思买、塔吉特、沃尔玛等公司&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21570383/price-matching-policy-apple-google-microsoft&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The亚马逊 10 月 Prime Day 活动的最佳早期优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23901327/amazon-october-prime-day-best-early-deals-tech-echo-speakers-fire- tvs-2023&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;PxtIa0&quot;>;在某些情况下，零售商会与亚马逊的定价匹配，这意味着您可以获得与 Prime 会员相同的折扣&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/ckJj2Ub5lJq&quot;>;Kindle Paperwhite&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/ckJj4U7ttHP&quot;>;Echo Pop&lt;/a>; 等产品。其他产品也有超值优惠，包括降噪耳机、平板电脑和智能手表。为了达成交易...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23905156/best-deals-anti-october-prime-day-walmart-best-buy-target -tech-2023&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23905156/best-deals-anti-october-prime-day-walmart-best-buy-target-tech-2023" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23905156/best-deals-anti-october-prime-day-walmart-best-buy-target-tech-2023</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-10T18:05:01-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-10T18:05:01-04:00</updated><title> Google Meet 增加了对 1080p 群组视频通话的支持</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google 多色“G”徽标的插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/IQHJoHMm2Z-bIGbDynJE0sIEE00=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72742350/STK093_Google_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：边缘&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;NdjJN3&quot;>;Google 正在启用以下功能：&lt; a href=&quot;https://workspaceupdates.googleblog.com/2023/10/full-hd-resolution-for-group-meetings-google-meet.html&quot;>;在群组通话期间流式传输 1080p 质量的网络摄像头视频&lt;/a>;对于工作区订阅者。该公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/4/26/23699733/google-meet-1080p-video-calls-hd&quot;>;首次启用&lt;/a>;高品质视频功能四月回来；然而，当时它只在一对一的会议中起作用。现在，该功能已扩展到包含三名或更多参与者的网络群组通话。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;BLsUuc&quot;>;要选择使用新功能，拥有全高清（或更好）网络摄像头的参与者将需要通过接受自动出现在加入屏幕上的提示来打开它。启用后，视频框右上角会出现 1080p 图标，以确认其已打开。如果启用的用户被固定或者观看者有足够大的屏幕，会议中的人员可以观看更高质量的视频...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2023/10/10/23911773/google-meet-workspace-1080p-full-hd-group-video-calls&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911773/google-meet-workspace-1080p-full-hd-group-video-calls" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911773/google-meet-workspace-1080p-full-hd-group-video-calls</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry></feed>